title: Kendall Jenner rocks the sports luxe trend in Milan | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share She teamed the garment with a pair of flared beige trousers whilst her scarlet stiletto boots peeked out beneath the item. Keeping her accessories simple, Kendall donned a floral cross body bag and a pair of chic cat eye shades. Au natural: The reality starlet, 21, went make-up free as she stepped out in the city showing off her natural beauty as she enjoyed a stroll Pretty in pink: Looking effortlessly chic, the Keeping Up With The Kardashians star donned a cropped pink hoodie for the outing which highlighted her slender waist Leggy lady! She teamed the garment with a pair of flared beige trousers whilst her scarlet stiletto boots peeked out beneath the item Earlier in the day Kendall led a charge of the models at the Fendi Fall/Winter 2017/18 where she dazzled in a striking scarlet coat. Keeping her look entirely themed, the star sported thigh-high leather boots underneath, which added a sexy edge to the otherwise covered up look, while also matching her stylish leather handbag. While her outfit was striking enough, the main pull was in her funky accessories, complete with huge round sunglasses and a pair of perspex red hoop earrings. Legs eleven! Kendall's supermodel pins were on parade as she strode on by All about the accessories: Keeping her accessories simple, Kendall donned a floral cross body bag and a pair of chic cat eye shades Brunette beauty: Kendall's raven coloured tresses were worn loose and poker straight in a centre parting that framed her pretty features Keeping her cool: Kendall was a vision of elegance and beauty as she headed out Making an entrance: Crowds gathered as Kendall headed out of her waiting car Although she has been storming the runway's at the Fashion Week's hottest shows, Kendall has no doubt been missing spending time with A$AP Rocky. Rumours of their union have long-been rife, with an insider recently telling Hollywood Life: 'Kendall is keeping her options open when it comes to dating. She’s really enjoying playing the field and not putting all of her eggs in one basket. 'She loves spending time with A$AP Rocky, 27, because he’s super creative and a great listener... But ultimately, having fun is her number one priority at the moment.'
